column2: Blaklader 1690 Rip Stop Pants with Stretch | Dark Navy
column3:
The Blaklader 1690 Rip Stop Pants with Stretch in dark navy offer lightweight durability and exceptional comfort. Therefore making them ideal for demanding work environments, especially during hot summer days. 

Constructed from a 7 oz ripstop fabric blend of 60% cotton and 40% polyester. However, these pants offer excellent breathability without losing its strength.

On the The Blaklader 1690 Rip Stop Pants the ripstop weave enhances tear resistance. This ensures the pants withstand tough use on the job site. Cordura® fabric reinforces the strength. This helps high-wear areas such as nail pockets, back pockets, ruler pocket, leg pockets, knees, hem. The design includes a side pocket for a tape measure. This reinforcement protects against wear and extends the lifespan of the pants. 

The Blaklader 1690 Rip Stop Pants also feature triple-stitched seams backed by a lifetime warranty, showing Blaklader’s commitment to quality and reliability. We've prioritized comfort and flexibility with a gusseted crotch panel made from stretch material, which allows for greater freedom of movement during physically demanding tasks.The pants are equipped with multiple functional pockets, including cargo and carpenter pockets on the legs, providing ample storage for tools and accessories. 

The Blaklader 1690 Rip Stop Pants with Stretch key features include:

  • Lightweight 7 oz ripstop fabric for breathability and durability.
  • Cordura® reinforcements on critical wear points for extended longevity.
  • Triple-stitched seams with lifetime warranty for superior strength.
  • Gusseted crotch panel with stretch fabric for enhanced mobility.
  • Multiple cargo and carpenter pockets for organized tool storage These pants combine expert craftsmanship with practical design, making them a reliable choice for professionals seeking durable, comfortable, and versatile workwear.
